Author: wild_banana_cookie
Text: I did weightlifting while in a deficit and seemed to still gain muscle as people has noticed it on me too. Although after awhile newbie gains go away and a surplus is needed.

Author: vdwednesday
Text: I did weightlifting in the beginning. You really don't built a lot of muscle when you are eating below maintenance, but it's a great booster for your metabolism and you don't get to look skinny fat
